---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro"
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Team from "../components/Team.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Smart Tech">
	<main class="space-y-20">
		<Container>
            <div class="relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center md:flex-row" id="about">
                <div class="row items-center py-5 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
                    <div class="text-center space-y-10">

                        <p class="text-5xl font-medium leading-none md:text-6xl">About Us</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">Boutique AI Architecture Agency.<br>End to end. Vendor agnostic. Customer focused.</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">We are a small, senior team of AI and data architects with deep delivery experience across energy, mining, government, finance, and media. We don't do superficial strategy decks — we design and build AI systems that work in production.</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">Our approach is vendor agnostic: we recommend the best tool for your problem, not the one tied to a partnership incentive. We work with Azure, AWS, GCP, and the leading open-source AI ecosystem — selecting what fits your context, budget, and team.</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">From AI strategy and architecture through to agentic systems, data platforms, and MLOps pipelines — we take full ownership of the outcome, not just the advice.</p>
                        <a class="px-9 py-5 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-white text-white hover:text-black border rounded-2xl justify-items-center md:justify-items-start gap-2.5 inline-flex"  href="/contact" target="_self">
                            <h2 class="text-center text-xl font-normal leading-7">Book a consultation</h2>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex-row items-center">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6">
                    <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/microsoft-partner-network.jpg" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="microsoft partner" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/solutions/aws-parner-logo.jpg" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="aws partner" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 flex grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/solutions/gcp-partner.png" class="h-9 w-auto m-auto" loading="lazy" alt="gcp partner" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/solutions/github-partner.png" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="github partner" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 flex grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/solutions/d365.jpg" class="h-8 w-auto m-auto" loading="lazy" alt="d365" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
                        <img src="/images/solutions/Salesforce.jpg" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="salesforce" width="" height="" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
        <Team/>
	</main>
</Layout>